					I will keep your information private throughout the study. I will
					record audio in the interviews, and take your name and store this
					information locally on my computer. Data will be anonymised in the
					final report and it won't be possible to identify individuals from the
					report. All collected data will be deleted on submission of the report
					(6th of May).
				</p>
